ANTI-PATTERNS
Never run a paid acquisition experiment when AR is below 40% — pouring water into a leaky bucket Never define "activated" as "completed signup" — activation = first experience of core value Never measure PLG success on traffic metrics — measure on aha moment completion rate Never build a viral loop without defining K-factor targets first 